Be a flight attendant with me.

55
00:04:11,468 --> 00:04:14,013
No, I'm going to work in a hotel.

56
00:04:14,096 --> 00:04:15,597
Come on. Why?

57
00:04:15,681 --> 00:04:16,932
I just like hotels.

58
00:04:18,726 --> 00:04:19,935
