95
00:07:10,328 --> 00:07:11,371
Hello?

96
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:16,459
Yes, I'm Number 511, Cheon Sa-rang.

97
00:07:19,504 --> 00:07:20,422
Sorry?

98
00:07:21,131 --> 00:07:22,215
Really?

99
00:07:24,259 --> 00:07:25,218
I did?

100
00:07:25,301 --> 00:07:26,344
